     <h1>Keeping Parking Lots CLean </h1> 
     <p>The college's Conditional Use Permit (Condition 99) requires, in order to minimze the runoff of debris and hazard chemicals into the storm drain system, that all employees and students be advised of the following:</p> 
     <ul> 
      <li>Littering is prohibited on campus.</li> 
      <li>Oil changing and other automotive repairs may only be performed at a designated environmentally-safe location at Physical Plant.</li> 
     </ul> 
     <p><a href="../physical_plant/vehicle-regulations.html">Click here</a> for the regulations governing the use of vehicles on campus.</p> 
     <p></p> 
